      • get

        GroundTerm[] get(int resultNo)
        Returns a substitution for all Variables.

        GroundTerms are ordered according to the Variables' first appearances in a depth-first, left-to-right traversal of the Formula in the DatabaseQuery that generated this ResultList.

        Parameters:
        resultNo - the index of the substitution (from 0 to size-1)
        Returns:
        the substituted GroundTerms
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if resultNo is out of range
